:32','2026-03-19 21:03:32','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=202',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(203,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/home-en/',0,'page','',0),(204,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','<p>The Ukrainian Sarcoma Foundation was established in 2024 with a mission to help sarcoma patients in Ukraine access quality diagnostics, treatment, and rehabilitation. Sarcoma is a rare form of cancer that affects bones and soft tissues, requiring specialized medical care that is often unavailable or unaffordable for many Ukrainian patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our foundation bridges the gap between patients and the medical resources they need. We fund diagnostic procedures, surgical implants, international consultations, and provide comprehensive support throughout the treatment journey.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since our founding, we have helped dozens of patients receive life-saving treatment, funded numerous surgeries, and organized international medical consultations with leading oncologists from the EU and USA.</p>','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-en','','','2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/about-en/',0,'page','',0),(205,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','','Our Activities','','publish','closed','closed','','activities-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/activities-en/',0,'page','',0),(206,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','<h2>Why early diagnosis matters?</h2>\r\n<p>Sarcoma is a rare disease that is often diagnosed at late stages due to low awareness among primary care physicians. Our foundation provides access to modern diagnostic methods for patients with suspected sarcoma.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we provide:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Biopsy and histological analysis</li>\r\n<li>MRI and CT imaging for precise tumor assessment</li>\r\n<li>PET-CT scanning for metastasis detection</li>\r\n<li>Immunohistochemical and genetic testing for sarcoma subtype identification</li>\r\n<li>Second opinion consultations with international pathologists</li>\r\n</ul>','Diagnostics','Providing access to modern sarcoma diagnostic methods for early disease detection.','publish','closed','closed','','diagnostics-en','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/diagnostics-en/',0,'page','',0),(207,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','<h2>Giving patients a chance at recovery</h2>\r\n<p>Surgical treatment of sarcoma often requires specialized oncological implants and endoprostheses that are extremely costly. Our foundation funds these critical surgical interventions to give patients a chance at recovery and improved quality of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our surgical support includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Oncological endoprostheses ŌĆö custom-made implants to replace bone affected by tumor</li>\r\n<li>Reconstructive surgery ŌĆö restoring function and appearance after tumor removal</li>\r\n<li>Bone transplantation ŌĆö using donor bone to replace removed segments</li>\r\n<li>Post-operative rehabilitation programs</li>\r\n</ul>','Implants &amp; Surgery','Funding surgical interventions, implants, and prostheses for sarcoma patients.','publish','closed','closed','','implants-operations-en','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/implants-operations-en/',0,'page','',0),(208,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','<h2>Access to global expertise</h2>\r\n<p>Complex sarcoma cases often require expertise that goes beyond what is available locally. Our foundation organizes international medical consultations, connecting Ukrainian patients with leading oncologists from the European Union and the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our consultation services:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expert consultations with EU and US specialists</li>\r\n<li>Second medical opinions for complex cases</li>\r\n<li>Telemedicine consultations ŌĆö remote access to world-class expertise</li>\r\n<li>Referrals to international clinics when necessary</li>\r\n</ul>','International Consultations','Organizing consultations with leading international oncologists for optimal treatment strategies.','publish','closed','closed','','international-consultations-en','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/international-consultations-en/',0,'page','',0),(209,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','','Reports','','publish','closed','closed','','reports-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/reports-en/',0,'page','',0),(210,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','','Partners','','publish','closed','closed','','partners-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/partners-en/',0,'page','',0),(211,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','','Donate','','publish','closed','closed','','donate-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:01','2026-03-19 21:28:01','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/donate-en/',0,'page','',0),(212,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:02','2026-03-19 21:28:02','','Knowledge Base','','publish','closed','closed','','blog-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:02','2026-03-19 21:28:02','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/blog-en/',0,'page','',0),(213,0,'2026-03-19 23:28:02','2026-03-19 21:28:02','','Contact Us','','publish','closed','closed','','contacts-en','','','2026-03-19 23:28:02','2026-03-19 21:28:02','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/contacts-en/',0,'page','',0),(226,1,'2026-03-20 00:10:18','2026-03-19 22:10:18','Maria is 8 years old and has been diagnosed with osteosarcoma. She needs urgent surgery to save her leg. The family cannot afford the treatment on their own.','Maria, 8 years old ŌĆö osteosarcoma','Needs urgent surgery.','publish','closed','closed','','ma