'2026-03-20 12:39:06','2026-03-20 10:39:06','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/about/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(273,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:06','2026-03-20 10:39:06','','Activities','','publish','closed','closed','','activities','','','2026-03-20 12:39:06','2026-03-20 10:39:06','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/activities/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(274,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','274','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/274/',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(275,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','','Surgery','','publish','closed','closed','','surgery','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/surgery/',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(276,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','','Consultations','','publish','closed','closed','','consultations','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/consultations/',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(277,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','','Cases','','publish','closed','closed','','cases','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/cases/',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(278,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/contact/',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(279,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','279','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/279/',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(280,0,'2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','280','','','2026-03-20 12:39:07','2026-03-20 10:39:07','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/280/',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(281,0,'2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','<p>The Ukrainian Sarcoma Foundation was established in 2024 with a mission to help sarcoma patients in Ukraine access quality diagnostics, treatment, and rehabilitation. Sarcoma is a rare form of cancer that affects bones and soft tissues, requiring specialized medical care that is often unavailable or unaffordable for many Ukrainian patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our foundation bridges the gap between patients and the medical resources they need. We fund diagnostic procedures, surgical implants, international consultations, and provide comprehensive support throughout the treatment journey.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since our founding, we have helped dozens of patients receive life-saving treatment, funded numerous surgeries, and organized international medical consultations with leading oncologists from the EU and USA.</p>','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','204-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','',204,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=281',0,'revision','',0),(282,0,'2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','<p>Early and accurate diagnosis is crucial for effective sarcoma treatment. Our foundation provides access to modern diagnostic methods including biopsy, MRI, CT, PET-CT scans, and genetic testing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We cover the costs of diagnostic procedures for patients who cannot afford them, ensuring that financial barriers do not prevent anyone from receiving a timely diagnosis. Our network of partner laboratories and medical centers across Ukraine and internationally enables us to provide world-class diagnostic services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we provide:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Biopsy and histological analysis</li>\r\n<li>MRI and CT imaging</li>\r\n<li>PET-CT scanning</li>\r\n<li>Genetic and immunohistochemical testing</li>\r\n<li>Second opinion consultations with international pathologists</li>\r\n</ul>','Diagnostics','','inherit','closed','closed','','206-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','',206,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=282',0,'revision','',0),(283,0,'2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','<p>Surgical treatment of sarcoma often requires specialized oncological implants and endoprostheses that are extremely costly. Our foundation funds these critical surgical interventions to give patients a chance at recovery and improved quality of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work with leading orthopedic oncology surgeons in Ukraine and abroad to ensure patients receive the best possible surgical care. From custom-made endoprostheses to reconstructive surgery, we cover the costs that patients and their families cannot bear alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our surgical support includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Oncological endoprostheses</li>\r\n<li>Reconstructive surgery</li>\r\n<li>Bone transplantation</li>\r\n<li>Post-operative rehabilitation programs</li>\r\n</ul>','Implants &amp; Surgery','','inherit','closed','closed','','207-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','',207,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=283',0,'revision','',0),(284,0,'2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','<p>Complex sarcoma cases often require expertise that goes beyond what is available locally. Our foundation organizes international medical consultations, connecting Ukrainian patients with leading oncologists from the European Union and the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through telemedicine platforms and in-person consultations, we ensure that every patient has access to the best medical minds, regardless of their location or financial situation. These consultations help determine optimal treatment strategies and can be life-changing for patients with rare or complex forms of sarcoma.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our consultation services:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expert consultations with EU and US specialists</li>\r\n<li>Second medical opinions</li>\r\n<li>Telemedicine consultations</li>\r\n<li>Referrals to international clinics when necessary</li>\r\n</ul>','International Consultations','','inherit','closed','closed','','208-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:33:03','2026-03-20 11:33:03','',208,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=284',0,'revision','',0),(285,0,'2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','<p>Early and accurate diagnosis is crucial for effective sarcoma treatment. Our foundation provides access to modern diagnostic methods including biopsy, MRI, CT, PET-CT scans, and genetic testing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We cover the costs of diagnostic procedures for patients who cannot afford them, ensuring that financial barriers do not prevent anyone from receiving a timely diagnosis. Our network of partner laboratories and medical centers across Ukraine and internationally enables us to provide world-class diagnostic services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we provide:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Biopsy and histological analysis</li>\r\n<li>MRI and CT imaging</li>\r\n<li>PET-CT scanning</li>\r\n<li>Genetic and immunohistochemical testing</li>\r\n<li>Second opinion consultations with international pathologists</li>\r\n</ul>','Diagnostics','Providing access to modern sarcoma diagnostic methods for early disease detection.','inherit','closed','closed','','206-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','',206,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=285',0,'revision','',0),(286,0,'2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','<p>Surgical treatment of sarcoma often requires specialized oncological implants and endoprostheses that are extremely costly. Our foundation funds these critical surgical interventions to give patients a chance at recovery and improved quality of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work with leading orthopedic oncology surgeons in Ukraine and abroad to ensure patients receive the best possible surgical care. From custom-made endoprostheses to reconstructive surgery, we cover the costs that patients and their families cannot bear alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our surgical support includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Oncological endoprostheses</li>\r\n<li>Reconstructive surgery</li>\r\n<li>Bone transplantation</li>\r\n<li>Post-operative rehabilitation programs</li>\r\n</ul>','Implants &amp; Surgery','Funding surgical interventions, implants, and prostheses for sarcoma patients.','inherit','closed','closed','','207-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','',207,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=286',0,'revision','',0),(287,0,'2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','<p>Complex sarcoma cases often require expertise that goes beyond what is available locally. Our foundation organizes international medical consultations, connecting Ukrainian patients with leading oncologists from the European Union and the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through telemedicine platforms and in-person consultations, we ensure that every patient has access to the best medical minds, regardless of their location or financial situation. These consultations help determine optimal treatment strategies and can be life-changing for patients with rare or complex forms of sarcoma.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our consultation services:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expert consultations with EU and US specialists</li>\r\n<li>Second medical opinions</li>\r\n<li>Telemedicine consultations</li>\r\n<li>Referrals to international clinics when necessary</li>\r\n</ul>','International Consultations','Organizing consultations with leading international oncologists for optimal treatment strategies.','inherit','closed','closed','','208-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:37:44','2026-03-20 11:37:44','',208,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=287',0,'revision','',0),(288,0,'2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','<h2>Why early diagnosis matters?</h2>\r\n<p>Sarcoma is a rare disease that is often diagnosed at late stages due to low awareness among primary care physicians. Our foundation provides access to modern diagnostic methods for patients with suspected sarcoma.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we provide:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Biopsy and histological analysis</li>\r\n<li>MRI and CT imaging for precise tumor assessment</li>\r\n<li>PET-CT scanning for metastasis detection</li>\r\n<li>Immunohistochemical and genetic testing for sarcoma subtype identification</li>\r\n<li>Second opinion consultations with international pathologists</li>\r\n</ul>','Diagnostics','Providing access to modern sarcoma diagnostic methods for early disease detection.','inherit','closed','closed','','206-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',206,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=288',0,'revision','',0),(289,0,'2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','<h2>Giving patients a chance at recovery</h2>\r\n<p>Surgical treatment of sarcoma often requires specialized oncological implants and endoprostheses that are extremely costly. Our foundation funds these critical surgical interventions to give patients a chance at recovery and improved quality of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our surgical support includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Oncological endoprostheses ŌĆö custom-made implants to replace bone affected by tumor</li>\r\n<li>Reconstructive surgery ŌĆö restoring function and appearance after tumor removal</li>\r\n<li>Bone transplantation ŌĆö using donor bone to replace removed segments</li>\r\n<li>Post-operative rehabilitation programs</li>\r\n</ul>','Implants &amp; Surgery','Funding surgical interventions, implants, and prostheses for sarcoma patients.','inherit','closed','closed','','207-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',207,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=289',0,'revision','',0),(290,0,'2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','<h2>Access to global expertise</h2>\r\n<p>Complex sarcoma cases often require expertise that goes beyond what is available locally. Our foundation organizes international medical consultations, connecting Ukrainian patients with leading oncologists from the European Union and the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our consultation services:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expert consultations with EU and US specialists</li>\r\n<li>Second medical opinions for complex cases</li>\r\n<li>Telemedicine consultations ŌĆö remote access to world-class expertise</li>\r\n<li>Referrals to international clinics when necessary</li>\r\n</ul>','International Consultations','Organizing consultations with leading international oncologists for optimal treatment strategies.','inherit','closed','closed','','208-revision-v1','','','2026-03-20 13:40:01','2026-03-20 11:40:01','',208,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=290',0,'revision','',0),(291,1,'2026-03-24 21:30:25','2026-03-24 19:30:25','','hero-surgery','','inherit','open','closed','','hero-surgery','','','2026-03-24 21:30:25','2026-03-24 19:30:25','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/hero-surgery.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(292,1,'2026-03-27 19:37:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','ą¦ąĄčĆąĮąŠą▓ąĖą║','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2026-03-27 19:37:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/?p=292',0,'post','',0),(293,1,'2026-03-27 19:39:21','2026-03-27 17:39:21','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ąĄą░ą╗ąĮą░</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','ą░ą▓čĆą░','','trash','closed','closed','','%d0%b0%d0%b2%d1%80%d0%b0__trashed','','','2026-03-27 19:41:34','2026-03-27 17:41:34','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/?post_type=case&#038;p=293',0,'case','',0),(294,1,'2026-03-27 19:41:56','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','ą¦ąĄčĆąĮąŠą▓ąĖą║','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2026-03-27 19:41:56','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/gproject/?post_type=case&p=294',0,'case','',0);
